sCQ_CANT_DETECT_SOUNDCARD_TITLE=Can't detect yer sound card
sCQ_CANT_DETECT_SOUNDCARD_DESC=Yer clockwork machine needs a sound card to make audio hails. Try our <a href="skype:?go#rescue.guides.soundsetupguide">sound setup guides</a> or plug in a headset that there comes with its own sound card.
sCQ_CANT_ACCESS_SOUNDCARD_TITLE=Can't access yer sound card
sCQ_CANT_ACCESS_SOUNDCARD_DESC=Skype needs to access yer clockwork machine's sound card to make hails. Try restarting yer clockwork machine to rescue Skype seek out yer sound card.
sCQ_MIC_ON_MUTE_OFF_CALL_TITLE=Yer voice horn be on silence the crew
sCQ_MIC_ON_MUTE_OFF_CALL_DESC=Ye need to un-silence the crew yer voice horn to make a hail. Select Automatically adjust voice horn ship's orders on this here screen. Then <a href="skype:?go#rescue.guides.soundsetupguide">inspect yer voice horn setup</a> on yer clockwork machine to make sure it's not muted in yer horn level ship's orders.
sCQ_MIC_ON_MUTE_ON_CALL_TITLE=Inspect yer voice horn
sCQ_MIC_ON_MUTE_ON_CALL_DESC=Plug in yer voice horn, switch it on, and inspect ye've selected it in yer voice horn ship's orders. Inspect yer mic isn't muted in yer clockwork machine's horn level ship's orders, or inspect  yer voice horn for a silence the crew switch and press it.
sCQ_CANT_ADJUST_MIC_OFF_CALL_TITLE=Skype can't adjust yer voice horn level
sCQ_CANT_ADJUST_MIC_OFF_CALL_DESC=Select Automatically adjust voice horn ship's orders on this here screen.
sCQ_CANT_ADJUST_MIC_ON_CALL_TITLE=Can't hear ye talking
sCQ_CANT_ADJUST_MIC_ON_CALL_DESC=Say something so Skype can detect yer voice horn.
sCQ_TURN_MIC_UP_TITLE=Turn yer voice horn up
sCQ_TURN_MIC_UP_DESC=Turn up the horn level on yer voice horn or select Automatically adjust voice horn ship's orders on this here screen.
sCQ_BACKGROUND_NOISE_TITLE=Ye've got background noise
sCQ_BACKGROUND_NOISE_DESC=Try moving to a quiet current port or muting yer voice horn when ye be not talking.
sCQ_MIC_WORKING_CORRECTLY_TITLE=Yer voice horn seems to be working fine
sCQ_MIC_WORKING_CORRECTLY_DESC=It's worth double-checking yer voice horn be switched on and correctly plugged in. Plus inspect it's not on silence the crew, and that there the horn level be high enough. For more rescue, visit the hail quality guide.
sCQ_SPEAKERS_ON_MUTE_OFF_CALL_TITLE=Yer sound horns be on silence the crew
sCQ_SPEAKERS_ON_MUTE_OFF_CALL_DESC=Ye need to unsilence the crew yer sound horns to make a hail. Select Automatically adjust sound horn ship's orders on this here screen. Then set forth yer clockwork machine's horn level controls and make sure nay devices be muted.
sCQ_SPEAKERS_ON_MUTE_ON_CALL_TITLE=Inspect yer sound horns
sCQ_SPEAKERS_ON_MUTE_ON_CALL_DESC=Be they on silence the crew? Inspect they're not muted in yer horn level ship's orders, or inspect yer sound horns for a silence the crew button and press it. Doesn't fix it? Make sure ye've selected the correct sound horns.
sCQ_SPEAKERS_TOO_LOUD_TITLE=Yer sound horns be too loud
sCQ_SPEAKERS_TOO_LOUD_DESC=Turn yer horn level down and move a little closer to yer voice horn. Then select Automatically adjust sound horn ship's orders on this here screen.
sCQ_SPEAKERS_WORKING_CORRECTLY_TITLE=Yer sound horns seem to be working fine
sCQ_SPEAKERS_WORKING_CORRECTLY_DESC=It's worth checking that there yer sound horns be switched on and correctly plugged in. Plus inspect they're not on silence the crew, and that there the horn level be high enough. For more rescue, visit the hail quality guide.
sCQ_CANT_DETECT_WEBCAM_TITLE=Can't detect yer spy glass
sCQ_CANT_DETECT_WEBCAM_DESC=If ye have a spy glass, make sure it's plugged in, switched on and ye've installed the latest drivers. Also try plugging it into a different USB port on yer clockwork machine, then relaunch Skype. For more rescue, go to the hail quality guide.
sCQ_CANT_CONNECT_TO_WEBCAM_TITLE=Skype can't set sail to yer spy glass
sCQ_CANT_CONNECT_TO_WEBCAM_DESC=Batten Down any other applications that there might be using yer spy glass. Ye could also plug yer spy glass into a different USB port on yer clockwork machine, then relaunch. For more rescue, inspect the hail quality guide.
sCQ_UNPLUG_USB_TITLE=Unplug some USB devices
sCQ_UNPLUG_USB_DESC=Drop Anchor any USB devices ye be not using or plug yer spy glass into a different USB port on yer clockwork machine.
sCQ_BAD_LIGHTING_TITLE=Bad lighting
sCQ_BAD_LIGHTING_DESC=Ye be not firin' away great spyglass feed right now because yer room be quite dark. Turn on more lights or set forth the curtains to let more light in. Plus make sure ye don't have a bright light or sunny window right behind ye.
sCQ_CAM_RECV_LOW_TITLE=Ye be receiving low quality spyglass feed
sCQ_CAM_RECV_LOW_DESC=This here be down to limitations of the other scallywag's spy glass, the open seas tether or clockwork machine speed. Not seeing their spyglass feed? They should try turning it off then on again, or plug their spy glass into a different USB port and restarting.
sCQ_CAM_SEND_LOW_OFF_CALL_TITLE=Yer spyglass feed quality be low
sCQ_CAM_SEND_LOW_OFF_CALL_DESC=Yer spy glass, the open seas tether or clockwork machine speed may be limiting the spyglass feed quality ye be able to fire away. Can't see yer spyglass feed? Make sure ye've installed the latest drivers, or plug yer spy glass into a different USB port and relaunch Skype.
sCQ_CAM_SEND_LOW_ON_CALL_TITLE=Yer spyglass feed quality be low
sCQ_CAM_SEND_LOW_ON_CALL_DESC=Speed up yer clockwork machine or the open seas tether to improve it. Or try a high quality spy glass. Not seeing each other's spyglass feed? Ye should both turn yer spyglass feed off then on again, or plug yer webcams into a different USB port and relaunch.
sCQ_CAM_RECV_MEDIUM_TITLE=Ye be receiving medium quality spyglass feed
sCQ_CAM_RECV_MEDIUM_DESC=This here be down to limitations of the other scallywag's spy glass, the open seas tether or clockwork machine speed. Not seeing their spyglass feed? Ask them to try turning it off then on again, or plugging their spy glass into a different USB port and restarting.
sCQ_CAM_SEND_MEDIUM_OFF_CALL_TITLE=Yer spyglass feed quality be medium
sCQ_CAM_SEND_MEDIUM_OFF_CALL_DESC=Speed up yer clockwork machine or the open seas tether to improve yer spyglass feed or use a high quality spy glass. Can't see yer spyglass feed? Make sure ye've installed the latest drivers, or plug yer spy glass into a different USB port and relaunch Skype.
sCQ_CAM_SEND_MEDIUM_ON_CALL_TITLE=Yer spyglass feed quality be medium
sCQ_CAM_SEND_MEDIUM_ON_CALL_DESC=Speed up yer clockwork machine or the open seas tether to improve it. Or try a high quality spy glass. Not seeing each other's spyglass feed? Ye should both turn yer spyglass feed off then on again, or plug yer webcams into a different USB port and relaunch.
sCQ_CAM_RECV_HIGH_TITLE=Ye be receiving high quality spyglass feed
sCQ_CAM_RECV_HIGH_DESC=Not seeing their spyglass feed? Ask them to try turning it off then on again, or plugging their spy glass into a different USB port and restarting.
sCQ_CAM_SEND_HIGH_OFF_CALL_TITLE=Yer spyglass feed quality be high
sCQ_CAM_SEND_HIGH_OFF_CALL_DESC=Ye be set up to make audio hails and high quality spyglass feed hails. Can't see yer spyglass feed? Make sure ye've installed the latest drivers, or plug yer spy glass into a different USB port and relaunch Skype.
sCQ_CAM_SEND_HIGH_ON_CALL_TITLE=Yer spyglass feed quality be high
sCQ_CAM_SEND_HIGH_ON_CALL_DESC=Not seeing each other's spyglass feed? Ye should both turn yer spyglass feed off then on again, or plug yer webcams into a different USB port and relaunch.
