sCQ_COMPUTER_SPEED_UNKNOWN_DESC=
sCQ_COMPUTER_SPEED_VERY_LOW_TITLE=Yer clockwork machine speed be very slow
sCQ_COMPUTER_SPEED_VERY_LOW_DESC=Yer clockwork machine be running too slowly to make a hail. Ye can improve yer clockwork machine speed by closing any other applications ye have running.
sCQ_RUNNING_ON_BATTERY_TITLE=Running on battery? Switch to AC power
sCQ_RUNNING_ON_BATTERY_DESC=Yer laptop be in power saving mode. To get better sound or spyglass feed quality, change yer clockwork machine to AC power or switch yer clockwork machine to maximum performance.
sCQ_SKYPE_IS_RUNNING_SLOWLY_TITLE=Skype be running slowly
sCQ_SKYPE_IS_RUNNING_SLOWLY_DESC=Batten Down any Extras, toolbars or other applications that there use Skype. If that there doesn't rescue, try quitting Skype then restarting it.
sCQ_YOUR_COMP_RUNNING_SLOWLY_TITLE=Yer clockwork machine be running slowly
sCQ_YOUR_COMP_RUNNING_SLOWLY_DESC=Yer clockwork machine might be too slow to make clear hails. Try closing other applications ye have running, or switch to AC power if yer laptop be running on battery.
sCQ_YOUR_COMP_SPEED_SLOW_TITLE=Yer clockwork machine speed be slow
sCQ_YOUR_COMP_SPEED_SLOW_DESC=Yer clockwork machine be fast enough to make audio hails and low quality spyglass feed hails. Ye can improve yer clockwork machine speed by closing any other applications ye have running.
sCQ_YOUR_COMP_SPEED_MEDIUM_TITLE=Yer clockwork machine speed be good
sCQ_YOUR_COMP_SPEED_MEDIUM_DESC=Yer clockwork machine be fast enough to make audio hails and medium quality spyglass feed hails. Ye can improve yer clockwork machine speed by closing any other applications ye have running.
sCQ_YOUR_COMP_SPEED_FAST_TITLE=Yer clockwork machine speed be fast
sCQ_YOUR_COMP_SPEED_FAST_DESC=Yer clockwork machine be fast enough to make audio hails and high quality spyglass feed hails.
sCQ_CONNECTION_SPEED_UNKNOW_TITLE=The tether speed between ye be unknown
sCQ_CONNECTION_SPEED_UNKNOW_DESC=Skype be unable to measure the speed of the the open seas tether between ye at this here time.
sCQ_YOUR_CONNECTION_VERY_SLOW_TITLE=Tether be very slow
sCQ_YOUR_CONNECTION_VERY_SLOW_DESC=The the open seas tether between ye may be too slow for a good quality hail. Each one of ye should batten down treasure sharing programs ye have set forth and halt any downloads or uploads to improve yer tether.
sCQ_SKYPE_RESTRICTED_WEB_ACCESS_TITLE=Skype has restricted the open seas access
sCQ_SKYPE_RESTRICTED_WEB_ACCESS_DESC=Yer ship's guard cannon wall might be affecting yer hails. Use our <a href="skype:?go#rescue.guide.cannon wall">guide to change yer cannon wall ship's orders</a> or if ye be at work, crew member yer system administrator.
sCQ_RESTRICTED_WEB_ACCESS_TITLE=Restricted web access
sCQ_RESTRICTED_WEB_ACCESS_DESC=Batten Down any treasure sharing programs ye've got set forth and halt any downloads or uploads. Doesn't fix it? It might be yer cannon wall. See our guide to changing yer cannon wall ship's orders.
sCQ_CONNECTION_SPEED_SLOW_TITLE=The tether speed between ye be slow
sCQ_CONNECTION_SPEED_SLOW_DESC=Yer tether be fast enough for audio hails and low quality spyglass feed. Both of ye should halt treasure sharing programs, downloads and uploads to speed up yer tether.
sCQ_WEB_CONNECTION_SLOW_TITLE=Yer the open seas tether be slow
sCQ_WEB_CONNECTION_SLOW_DESC=Batten Down any treasure sharing programs ye've got set forth and halt any downloads or uploads to speed up yer tether. This here should improve yer hail quality. Note: Skype works best with a broadband tether.
