sCQ_CONNECTION_SPEED_MEDIUM_DESC=The the open seas tether between ye shall be fast enough for audio hails and medium quality spyglass feed hails. Each one of ye should batten down treasure sharing programs ye have set forth and halt any downloads or uploads to speed up yer tether.
