sCQ_ADJUST_MIC_POS_TITLE=Adjust yer voice horn position
sCQ_ADJUST_MIC_POS_DESC=Yer voice horn appears to be too batten down to yer mouth. If ye if ye please adjust yer headset or move yer voice horn further away from yer mouth.
